arStrings.szText:
{icon:bullet} Your attacks deal {c_random}[SF_9|1]%{/c} of your Maximum Life as Physical damage to nearby enemies. This effect can occur once every {c_number}[SF_10]{/c} seconds.

{icon:bullet} You heal for {c_number}[SF_7|1]%{/c} of your Maximum Life for each enemy damaged this way.
